OL,6,F"We urge anyone affected by
OL,7,Fyesterday's events to seek support,
OL,8,Fand not to share any videos, photos or
OL,9,Finformation that might cause further
OL,10,Fdistress to pupils or parents at the
OL,11,Fschool."
OL,13,FThe south-west Wales school went into
OL,14,Flockdown after a "code red" alarm
OL,15,Fsounded through the PA system, during
OL,16,Fwhich students and staff are said to
OL,17,Fhave hidden in classrooms ` with one
OL,18,Fpupil reportedly vaulting the school
OL,19,Ffence to get to safety.
