OL,6,FThe lockdown lasted around four hours
OL,7,Fbetween 11.20am and 3.20pm, resulting
OL,8,Fin a lengthy and anxious wait for
OL,9,Fparents who were seen tearfully
OL,10,Fhugging their children after they
OL,11,Fwalked through the gates.
OL,13,FAll three victims were taken to
OL,14,Fhospital with stab wounds but Dyfed-
OL,15,FPowys Police said their injuries were
OL,16,Fnot life-threatening.
